snippet.title: Freaked Fleapit - Official Demo Launch Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description:
Freaked Fleapit is an action-rhythm roguelike dating simulation game developed by Finch Bird Studio. Players will dance through the 9 circles of Hell, date potential lovers, and escape Purgatory. Freaked Fleapitis launching soon for PC with a demo on Steam available now.

#Games #Gaming #GameTrailers
